PAP Link App is used for BMC’s sleep therapy and ventilation devices to check treatment effect and get treatment report.

· Simply scan the QR code to obtain the treatment data;
· Easily check the compliance details on your phone;
· Automatically forward treatment report to your doctor or healthcare provider to get further helpful guidance.

Firstly, use the PAP Link App to scan the “iCode QR / QR+” on the device screen. After scanning, the App will identify device Serial Number automatically, thus the binding is finished;
Secondly, go to “My Page”, input email addresses (e.g. the user’s, doctor’s and healthcare provider’s, maximum 3 email addresses). The treatment report in PDF file will be sent to those emails automatically after each scanning.

In the “Report” page, you can check the treatment details, which contains usage days, compliance time, AHI and treatment pressure etc.
